Chongqing secondary vocational school pilot modern apprenticeship enrollment is the enterprise quasi-employee-xinhuanet yesterday, the reporter learned from the municipal education commission, this year, the city will be in 60 secondary vocational schools pilot "modern apprenticeship" talent training model, accept the pilot training students at the same time have apprenticeship status, enrollment after the entry will be pre-recorded as the pilot enterprise employees. The municipal education commission requirements, standardize secondary vocational school enrollment and enterprise employment procedures,To clarify the dual status of apprentice secondary vocational school students and enterprise prospective employees, according to the principle of two-way selection, apprentices, schools and enterprises sign a tripartite agreement. For apprentices who have reached the age of 16 but not 18, apprentices, guardians, schools and enterprises must sign an agreement to determine the rights and interests of all parties and the specific posts and teaching contents of apprentice on-the-job training.Rights and interests protection. Encourage pilot schools to adopt the form of modern apprenticeship and cooperative enterprises to jointly carry out pre-job training and job-transfer training for enterprise employees. Pilot schools should reform the talent training model. The school and enterprise jointly design the talent training plan, jointly formulate the professional teaching standards, curriculum standards, post standards, enterprise master standards, quality control standards and corresponding implementation plans. The pilot takes the training system as a pilot cycle, and the internship time of students in the enterprise is determined according to the professional talent training plan. The internship is generally 6 months. In the enterprise practice, the enterprise team management mode should be implemented. According to the characteristics of different majors, one master can lead 2~5 apprentices.Form a study group to ensure that students are proficient in the skills required for each rotation training position. According to the arrangement, from 2016 to August 2019, our city will determine 60 municipal modern apprenticeship pilot projects in three batches, with about 50 people in each pilot, and a total of about 3000 students will be trained.(Apprentice). In accordance with the principle of pilot first, then implementation, and gradual promotion from point to surface, explore the establishment of a long-term mechanism of joint enrollment, joint training and integrated education between schools and enterprises, effectively improve students 'post skills, and improve students' corresponding employment rate and employment quality.
